skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: fencing match
des: Find local fencing tournaments in your area or anywhere throughout the United States. Get information on future tournaments or hear the results from past events. Search tournaments containing foil, saber, or epee events. Or filter by men, women, mixed or by rating such as C and under or by using cadet, junior, open, senior, or veteran. Once you have your list, pick a tournament (say "select" followed by the tournament number) to get a list of matching events. Then get the fencers or results for one of the events (say "select" followed by the number of the event).
